    "description": "IDP Education India International Enterprises, one of India's leading organizations, is hiring a Teacher for our Surat operations. We offer a competitive salary package along with world-class benefits.\n\nAbout IDP Education India International Enterprises:\nIDP Education India International Enterprises is a leading organization in the Hybrid sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Coordinate with academic counselors for student career guidance\n• Participate in school events, workshops, and training programs\n• Utilize technology and digital tools to enhance learning outcomes\n• Monitor student progress and provide timely feedback\n• Conduct doubt-clearing sessions and remedial classes for weak students\n• Create curriculum-aligned learning materials and assessments\n• Participate in teacher training and professional development programs\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• B.Ed / M.Ed from a recognized institution\n• 0-1 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Content Creation\n• Proficiency in Curriculum Development\n• Proficiency in Special Education\n• Proficiency in Bloom's Taxonomy\n• Proficiency in Lesson Planning\n• Proficiency in Educational Technology\n• Proficiency in Classroom Management\n• Proficiency in Research Skills\n\nWork Mode: Hybrid - Flexible work-from-home and office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• Comprehensive health insurance for self and family\n• Life and accident insurance\n• Modern office with recreational facilities\n• Transportation and conveyance allowance\n• Salary Range: 2.5 LPA - 6 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Surat, Gujarat, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with IDP Education India International Enterprises!",
